Class OriginalFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.saxon.functions.AbstractFunction

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callable, ContextOriginator, Function, GroundedValue, Item, Sequence

    public class OriginalFunction
extends AbstractFunction
implements Function, ContextOriginator
    This class represents a function invoked using xsl:original from within an xs:override element.
